				DesignBuilder is arguably the most advanced and user-friendly building performance analysis software available in the world today. It is versatile and can be used for a number of purposes, including building energy assessment, thermal comfort prediction, natural ventilation estimation, and daylight level calculation.
			</p>
			<p>
				Greenplan has partnered with DesignBuilder UK to ensure that South Africa has access to the best tools on the market.  As the sole South African agent for <%= link_to "DesignBuilder Software", "http://www.designbuilder.co.uk/" %> we provide sales, technical support and training in Southern Africa.
