			<p>
				DesignBuilder provides advanced modelling tools in an easy-to-use interface. This enables both architects and engineers to use the same software to develop comfortable and energy-efficient building designs from concept through to completion. You can build up models from scratch, using DXF or PDF 2-D drawings or importing 3-D models via gbXML format.
			</p>


